CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 13, 1962, pg. A16, reads: "The D.I.'s - The scintillating D.I.s readying plans for their Jan. 28 date at the Holiday House, introduce two new members, shown above. Left: Hilda Logan and Evelyn Christian begin to work at once with members Nellye Barron, Juanita Drake, Margaret Watson and Gloria Grate.  All members are available for tickets. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Six members of D. I. Club, from left: Hilda Logan, Evelyn Christian, Nellye Barron, Juanita Drake, Margaret Watson, and Gloria Golden Grate gathered at table planning "Melody in Fashion" MENDS benefit at Holiday House
